 the machine  Use the shop vac to remove dust from cutting after every job  Make sure to vacuum all areas  taking great care around the tool Changing tools  Wrenches are kept on the left side of the machine The locating cycle for the Z axis needs to be performed after each change  Use the wizard in VPanel  be sure to use the correct one Comments are closed Site Administration Log in Entries RSS Comments RSS WordPress org Nirvana   WordPress 